  N5 --> Z1[Outcome: Reduced slow-moving inventory, improved EBITDA/COGS alignment with demand signals, optimized multi-echelon safety stock, auditable decision trail for approvals/overrides, and measurable reduction in excess days-of-supply and procurement cost deltas.]
